anical Switch with 45 G actuation force&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;100 million keystroke lifespan&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Chroma backlighting with 16.8 million customizable color options&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Underglow lighting with 38 customization zones&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Ergonomic Wrist Rest with 20 customization zones underglow&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Multi-functional digital dial&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Dedicated media controls&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Hybrid onboard storage – up to 5 profiles&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Razer Synapse 3 enabled&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Fully programmable keys with on-the-fly macro recording&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;10 key roll-over with anti-ghosting&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Gaming mode option&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Braided Fiber Cable&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;1000 Hz Ultrapolling&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Aluminum matte top plate&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;/ul&gt;","false","0","00010224","8480","-1","true","","-1","-1","true","24","Měsíc(ů)","","0001-01-01T00:00:00","4313.00","KS","0.00","19","2018-07-19T09:25:42.17","RAZ","43","true","0","{'0':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0a_3.jpg','1':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0b_3.jpg','2':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0c_3.jpg','3':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0d_3.jpg','4':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0e_3.jpg','5':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0f_3.jpg','6':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0g_3.jpg','7':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0h_3.jpg','8':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0i_3.jpg','9':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0j_3.jpg','10':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0k_3.jpg','11':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0l_3.jpg','12':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0m_3.jpg','13':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMGCACHE\/_1261\/1261893_0n_3.jpg','14':'https:\/\/c.edsystem.cz\/IMG